---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="About FastClickTest — Free Online CPS Test Tool"
  description="Learn about FastClickTest.com — the cleanest, most accurate free click speed test online. Built for gamers, Minecraft players, and anyone testing their CPS."
  currentPage="about"
>
<div class="page">

  <div class="page-hero">
    <h1>About <span class="hi">FastClickTest</span></h1>
    <p>The cleanest, most complete free click speed test on the internet — built for gamers, by gamers.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="seo-content">

    <h2>Why We Built FastClickTest</h2>
    <p>
      Every click speed test we found was the same story — cluttered with ads, slow to load,
      missing features gamers actually care about, and built on designs that haven't been updated
      since 2012. We built FastClickTest to be the CPS test we always wanted: fast, clean, dark by
      default, and genuinely useful for anyone who wants to know how fast they can click.
    </p>

    <h3>What Makes Us Different</h3>
    <p>
      Most click speed tests show you a number when the test ends. FastClickTest shows you a
      <strong>live CPS graph as you click</strong> — so you can see exactly when you peaked and when
      fatigue set in. Your <strong>personal best is saved locally</strong> in your browser with no
      account required. We offer <strong>more test modes</strong> than any competitor: 1s, 5s, 10s,
      15s, 30s, 60s, plus the unique 100-click challenge where you race to 100 clicks as fast as possible.
    </p>

    <h3>All Our Free Tools</h3>
    <p>
      We cover every major clicking benchmark in one place — the standard <a href="/">CPS test</a>,
      the <a href="/kohi-click-test">Kohi click test</a> (original Minecraft PvP benchmark),
      <a href="/jitter-click-test">jitter click test</a>, <a href="/butterfly-click-test">butterfly
      click test</a>, <a href="/drag-click-test">drag click test</a>,
      <a href="/right-click-test">right-click CPS test</a>,
      <a href="/spacebar-test">spacebar speed test</a>, and our unique
      <a href="/reaction-time-test">reaction time test</a>. All free, all instant, no account needed.
    </p>

    <h3>Privacy First</h3>
    <p>
      Your scores are saved in your browser's localStorage — nothing is sent to any server. We don't
      track individual clicks, store results in a database, or require any account to use any feature.
      See our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> for full details.
    </p>

    <h3>Get in Touch</h3>
    <p>
      Found a bug? Have a suggestion for a new test? We read every message.
      Use our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a> to reach us — we typically respond within 24–48 hours.
    </p>

  </div>

</div>
</Layout>
